## ğŸ“„ Project: Dynamic Scroll Scraper (`dynamic_scroll_scraper.py`)

### ğŸ› ï¸ Key Skill Focus

|     Skill                |                    Description                 |                        Technical Implementation |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Browser Control** | Initializes and manages a Chrome browser instance to simulate a real user.   | `Selenium WebDriver` |
| **Explicit Waits** | Essential for dynamic scraping; pauses until data is fully rendered.          | `WebDriverWait` |
| **User Simulation** | Mimics human scrolling to trigger infinite load sequences.                   | `window.scrollTo` |

